    "spotlight_message": "Say hello si {name}!",
    "dbq_title": "iwe ṣẹ-Ti o da lori ibeere",
    "dbq_text": "iwe ṣẹ-Ti o da lori ibeere: akẹkọọ ṣe atupale primary sources, build evidence-ti o da lori arguments, ati ṣe adaṣe central imọ ti awùjọ-studies + ELA idanwo. Generates orisun iwe ṣẹ, scaffolded ibeere, ati idahun keys aligned si rẹ eto.",
