    "glossary_scramble": "Tún àwọn lẹ́tà tó dàrú dọ́gba sí ọ̀rọ̀ tó tọ́. Ó ń kọ́ akọsílẹ̀ ọ̀rọ̀ àti ìmọ̀ àpẹẹrẹ lẹ́tà.",
    "glossary_edit": "Ṣii iwe ọrọ editor si ṣatunṣe awọn ọrọ akoonu. Editor allows: modifying ọrọ names ati itumọ, adding/removing ọrọ, regenerating individual aworan, adjusting itumọ, ati reordering ọrọ. Changes pamọ automatically. Lo nigba ti: AI-ti ṣẹda itumọ need refinement, ọrọ jẹ incorrect tabi missing, tabi adding akẹkọọ-suggested awọn ọrọ. Ṣatunṣe ọna fihan: full ọrọ kaadi ninu list wo, inline editing fun yara changes, ati bulk actions fun ọ̀pọ̀lọpọ̀ ọrọ. imọran: Review ati ṣatunṣe AI itumọ si match rẹ pato curriculum context.",
