      "role_of_a_species_in_its_ecosystem_two": "Ipa species nínú ecosystem rẹ̀. species méjì kò lè gba niche kannáà (competitive exclusion).",
      "physical_place_where_an_organism_lives": "Ibi ti organism ń gbé.",
      "network_of_who_eats_whom_trophic_level": "Nẹ́tíwọ́ọ̀kì ti ẹni tí ń jẹ ẹni. Trophic level — producer → primary consumer → secondary → àti bẹ́ẹ̀ bẹ́ẹ̀ lọ.",
      "make_own_food_plants_algae_some_bacter": "Ń ṣe oúnjẹ ara wọn. Ọ̀gbìn, algae, bakitéríà kan. Ìpìlẹ̀ food chain.",
      "get_food_by_eating_others_herbivores_c": "Ń rí oúnjẹ nípa jíjẹ àwọn mìíràn. Herbivore, carnivore, omnivore.",
      "break_down_dead_matter_fungi_bacteria_": "Ń fọ́ ohun tí ó kú. Elú, bakitéríà, decomposer. Ń ṣe recycle oúnjẹ.",
      "close_interaction_between_species_mutu": "Ìbáṣepọ̀ tímọ́tímọ́ láàrin species. Mutualism (+/+), commensalism (+/0), parasitism (+/−).",
