      "warm_lo_fi_keys": "Warm lo-fi keys",
      "barry_harris_1929_2021_codified_bebop_": "Barry Harris (1929-2021) ṣe àgbékalẹ̀ harmony bebop lọ́nà tó tọ́. Ètò rẹ̀ ń lo 6th chords dípò 7ths ó sì ń fi diminished passing chords sáàrin àwọn digiri scale fún ìdarí ohùn tó dán.",
      "ii_v_i_jazz": "ii-V-I (Jazz)",
      "12_bar_blues": "12-Bar Blues",
      "vi_iv_i_v_emo_alt": "vi-IV-I-V (Emo/Alt)",
      "1st_overtone": "Overtone 1k",
      "2nd_overtone": "Overtone 2k",
      "3rd_overtone": "Overtone 3k",
      "4th_overtone": "Overtone 4k",
      "5th_overtone": "Overtone 5k",
      "6th_overtone": "Overtone 6k",
      "7th_overtone": "Overtone 7k",
      "attack_time_to_reach_full_volume_decay": "Attack: àkókò láti dé volume kíkún. Decay: àkókò láti sọ̀kalẹ̀ sí sustain. Sustain: ìpele volume tí a dì mú. Release: àkókò tó ń rẹ̀wẹ̀sì lẹ́yìn tí a tú key sílẹ̀.",
      "a_scale_is_an_ordered_set_of_pitches_m": "Scale jẹ́ àkójọ pitches tó ní ètò. Modes jẹ́ ìyíká scale tó ń bẹ̀rẹ̀ láti orí àwọn digiri ọ̀tọ̀ọ̀tọ̀. Ọ̀kọ̀ọ̀kan ń dá ìmọ̀lára ọ̀tọ̀ sílẹ̀.",
      "chords_are_built_by_stacking_intervals": "A ń kọ́ chords nípa kíkó intervals (3rds) lé ara wọn. Major ń lo major 3rd + minor 3rd. Minor ń yí wọn padà. Extended chords ń fi 7ths, 9ths, àti jù bẹ́ẹ̀ lọ kún.",
      "kicks_use_a_sine_oscillator_with_a_pit": "Kicks ń lo sine oscillator pẹ̀lú pitch sweep. Snares ń dàpọ̀ noise (filtered) + tone body. Hi-hats ń lo high-pass filtered noise bursts.",
      "4_4_4_quarter_note_beats_per_bar_most_": "4/4 = quarter-note beats 4 fún bar kọ̀ọ̀kan (èyí tó wọ́pọ̀ jù). 3/4 = ìmọ̀lára waltz. 6/8 = compound duple. 5/4 àti 7/8 ń dá grooves aláìdọ́gba, àjèjì sílẹ̀.",
      "keys_arranged_by_ascending_5ths_clockw": "A ṣètò keys nípa 5ths tó ń gòkè ní ọ̀nà aago. Keys tó wà nítòsí ń pín note 6 nínú 7. Lílọ ní ọ̀nà aago ń fi sharps kún; ìdàkejì aago ń fi flats kún.",
      "every_musical_sound_contains_overtones": "Gbogbo ohùn orin ní overtones lókè fundamental. Agbára ìbátan wọn ń pinnu timbre — ìdí nìyẹn tí kàkàkí fi ń dún yàtọ̀ sí fèrè ní pitch kan náà.",
      "an_interval_is_the_distance_between_tw": "Interval jẹ́ ààlà láàrin pitches méjì, tí a ń wọ̀n ní semitones. Frequency ratio ń pinnu consonance (ratios tó rọrùn bíi 3:2 ń dún jẹ́ẹ́jẹ́ẹ́).",
      "plays_chord_notes_one_at_a_time_in_seq": "Ń tú notes chord ní ọ̀kọ̀ọ̀kan ní ọ̀wọ̀. Òkè = láti ìsàlẹ̀ sí òkè, Ìsàlẹ̀ = láti òkè sí ìsàlẹ̀. Ń dá patterns tó ń ṣàn láti chords tó dúró jẹ́ẹ́.",
      "a_filter_removes_frequencies_above_low": "Filter ń yọ frequencies tó wà lókè (lowpass), nísàlẹ̀ (highpass), tàbí yíká (bandpass) cutoff frequency. Resonance (Q) ń mú frequencies nítòsí cutoff pọ̀ sí i, ó ń dá peak sílẹ̀.",
      "tremolo_periodic_volume_changes_amplit": "Tremolo: àwọn ìyípadà volume ìgbà dé ìgbà (amplitude modulation). Vibrato: àwọn ìyípadà pitch ìgbà dé ìgbà (frequency modulation). Àwọn méjèèjì ni LFO (Low Frequency Oscillator) ń darí.",
      "discovered_in_1983_a_noise_burst_feeds": "A ṣàwárí rẹ̀ ní 1983. Noise burst ń wọ inú delay line kúkúrú gan-an tó ní feedback. Delay time ń pinnu pitch. Filter nínú feedback loop ń darí ìmọ́lẹ̀ àti decay. Ó ń fara wé plucked strings lọ́nà àdánidá.",
      "the_sequencer_is_a_composition_tool_ea": "Sequencer jẹ́ ohun èlò ìṣẹ̀dá orin. Step kọ̀ọ̀kan dúró fún subdivision beat. Ẹsẹ̀ melody ń ṣètò pitched notes, ìlù ń fi rhythm kún. Musical notation ń fi ohun tí o dá hàn.",
      "notes_on_lines_and_spaces_represent_pi": "Notes tó wà lórí ìlà àti àyè ń dúró fún pitches. A ń fi ìpẹ̀ note hàn duration: whole (○), half (𝅗𝅥), quarter (♩), eighth (♪). Staff ní ìlà 5.",
