      "play_piano_keys_presets": "Tú — piano keys + presets",
      "equal_temperament_12_notes_per_octave_": "Equal temperament: notes 12 fún octave, ratio 2^(1/12). A4 = 440 Hz; A5 = 880 Hz. Well-Tempered Clavier ti Bach (1722) yí ayé lérò padà nípa ìfohùnṣọ̀kan yìí. Gbogbo note tí o ń tú níbí wà lórí grid yẹn.",
      "scales_the_major_minor_modal_grammar": "Scales — gírámà major + minor + modal",
      "major_w_w_h_w_w_w_h_minor_w_h_w_w_h_w_": "Major: W-W-H-W-W-W-H. Minor: W-H-W-W-H-W-W. Modes 7 (Ionian, Dorian, Phrygian, Lydian, Mixolydian, Aeolian, Locrian) ń wá láti inú ìyí interval pattern ti major scale.",
      "chords_stacked_thirds_inversions": "Chords — stacked thirds + inversions",
      "triads_root_third_fifth_major_4_3_semi": "Triads: root + third + fifth. Major (4+3 semitones), minor (3+4), diminished (3+3), augmented (4+4). 7th chords ń fi third mìíràn kún. Pop music = ~chords 6 tó ń tún ara wọn ṣe; jazz ń lo extensions àti substitutions.",
      "harmony_pad_voiced_pads_drones": "Harmony Pad — voiced pads + drones",
      "sustained_chord_textures_the_bed_under": "Sustained chord textures — ibùsùn tó wà lábẹ́ ó fẹ́rẹ̀ẹ́ jẹ́ gbogbo cinematic score. Gbìyànjú iv-V-i ní minor, tàbí i-VI-VII fún ìmọ̀lára Hans Zimmer. Drones ní fifths ń ti egwú classical India àti àṣà bagpipe lẹ́yìn.",
      "beat_pad_sample_based_drums": "Beat Pad — sample-based drums",
      "most_popular_music_sits_at_4_4_90_130_": "Ọ̀pọ̀ orin gbajúmọ̀ wà ní 4/4, 90-130 BPM. Hip-hop ~85-95, house 120-130, drum-and-bass ~170 (ìmọ̀lára half-time). Kick ní 1+3, snare ní 2+4 = backbeat — ìpìlẹ̀ rock + pop.",
      "theory_the_math_behind_the_sound": "Theory — ìṣirò lẹ́yìn ohùn",
      "pythagoras_500_bce_discovered_consonan": "Pythagoras (~500 BCE) ṣàwárí consonance láti inú integer frequency ratios: octave 2:1, fifth 3:2, fourth 4:3. Helmholtz gbòòrò rẹ̀ ní 1862. Ohùn = compression waves; orin = patterns tí a fohùnṣọ̀kan láti pè ní ẹlẹ́wà.",
