      "fm_synthesis_2": "FM Synthesis",
      "frequency_modulation_fm_synthesis_uses": "Frequency Modulation (FM) synthesis ń lo oscillator kan (modulator) láti yí frequency ti òmíràn (carrier) padà kíákíá. Ratio modulator:carrier ń pinnu harmonic content. Ratios tó rọrùn (1:1, 2:1, 3:1) ń dá harmonic tones. Ratios tó díjú ń dá metallic, bell-like, tàbí inharmonic sounds. Yamaha DX7 ló mú FM gbajúmọ̀ ní 1983.",
      "bright": "Ìmọ́lẹ̀",
