      "arpeggiator_gate": "Gate ti arpeggiator",
      "an_arpeggiator_plays_the_notes_of_a_ch": "🔬 Arpeggiator ń tú notes chord ní ọ̀kọ̀ọ̀kan ní ọ̀wọ̀. \"Òkè\" ń lọ láti ìsàlẹ̀ sí òkè, ó ń dá agbára tó ń gòkè. \"Ìsàlẹ̀\" ń sọ̀kalẹ̀ fún ìmọ̀lára ìṣàn omi. Ìyára ń darí eré (kékeré = kíákíá). Gate ń darí bí note kọ̀ọ̀kan ṣe ń dún tó (100% = legato, 10% = staccato). Gbìyànjú ìyára=100ms + octaves 4 + up pattern fún classic trance arp!",
      "live_mic_effects_lab": "🎤 Live Mic Effects Lab",
      "sing_speak_or_play_an_instrument_hear_": "Kọ orin, sọ̀rọ̀, tàbí tú ohun èlò — gbọ́ effects lẹ́sẹ̀kẹsẹ̀!",
      "monitor_hear_yourself_use_headphones": "🔊 Monitor (gbọ́ ara rẹ — lo headphones!)",
      "microphone_monitor_volume": "Volume monitor microphone",
      "how_effects_change_sound_waves": "🔬 Bí Effects Ṣe Ń Yí Sound Waves Padà",
      "filter_cutoff": "Filter (Cutoff)",
      "removes_frequencies_above_lowpass_or_b": "Ń yọ frequencies tó wà lókè (lowpass) tàbí nísàlẹ̀ (highpass) threshold. Bíi fífi ọwọ́ bò ẹnu — frequencies gíga ń parẹ́, ohùn ń di \"ṣú\" síi.",
      "delay": "Delay",
      "creates_echoes_by_copying_the_signal_a": "Ń dá echoes nípa dídà signal kọ àti títú un padà lẹ́yìn àkókò kúkúrú. Feedback ń darí iye echoes tó ń tún ṣe.",
      "reverb_2": "Reverb",
      "simulates_room_acoustics_by_creating_t": "Ń fara wé acoustics yàrá nípa dídá ẹgbẹẹgbẹ̀rún echoes kékéké tó ń dàpọ̀. Yàrá kékeré = reverb kúkúrú, katidira = reverb gígùn.",
      "distortion": "Distortion",
      "clips_the_waveform_peaks_turning_smoot": "Ń gé peaks waveform, ó ń yí sine waves tó dán padà sí àwọn ìrísí líle, oníhà. Èyí ń fi harmonics tuntun tí kò sí nínú ohùn ìpilẹ̀ṣẹ̀ kún.",
      "chorus": "Chorus",
      "duplicates_the_signal_with_a_slight_co": "Ń dà signal kọ pẹ̀lú delay kékeré tó ń yípadà nígbà gbogbo. Èyí ń fara wé voices/ohun èlò púpọ̀ tó ń tú papọ̀ láìbára mu díẹ̀.",
      "tremolo": "Tremolo",
      "rapidly_varies_the_volume_up_and_down_": "Ń yí volume padà sókè àti sísàlẹ̀ kíákíá, ó ń dá ipa lílù sílẹ̀. Ó wọ́pọ̀ ní surf guitar àti orin organ.",
      "use_headphones_when_monitoring_to_avoi": "Lo headphones nígbà monitoring láti yẹra fún feedback loops! Mic ń kọjá gbogbo effects tó wà lókè (filter, delay, reverb, àti bẹ́ẹ̀ bẹ́ẹ̀ lọ) — ṣàtúnṣe wọn láti gbọ́ bí ọ̀kọ̀ọ̀kan ṣe ń yí ohùn tàbí ohun èlò rẹ padà.",
      "connect_your_microphone_to_run_your_vo": "So microphone rẹ pọ̀ láti mú ohùn tàbí ohun èlò rẹ kọjá effects chain lẹ́sẹ̀kẹsẹ̀.",
      "see_your_voice_as_a_waveform_frequency": "Wo ohùn rẹ bíi waveform + frequency spectrum. Gbọ́ bí filter, delay, reverb, distortion, àti chorus ṣe ń yí sound waves padà ní ti ara.",
      "xy_performance_pad": "🎯 XY Performance Pad",
      "touch_drag_x_pitch_y_filter_effect": "Fọwọ́kàn & fa — X = pitch, Y = filter/effect",
      "xy_pad_performance": "XY Pad Performance",
      "the_xy_pad_maps_your_finger_mouse_posi": "XY pad ń ṣàpèjúwe ipò ìka/mouse rẹ sí musical parameters lẹ́sẹ̀kẹsẹ̀. X axis ń darí pitch (òsì = ìsàlẹ̀, ọ̀tún = òkè). Y axis ń darí filter cutoff frequency (òkè = ìmọ́lẹ̀, ìsàlẹ̀ = ṣú). Èyí jọ ohun èlò bíi Korg Kaoss Pad, tó yí live electronic music performance padà nípa yíyí 2D gestures sí ohùn.",
      "xy_performance_pad_left_right_is_pitch": "XY performance pad. Òsì–ọ̀tún ni pitch, òkè–ìsàlẹ̀ ni filter brightness. Lo arrow keys láti gbìmọ̀ àti tú note; tẹ Escape tàbí Space láti dúró.",
